#: ../../docs/schema/reference.md:440
msgid ""
"If the [Quantities, Units, Dimensions and Data Types "
"Ontologies](http://www.qudt.org/qudt/owl/1.0.0/unit/) unit classification "
"scheme is used, then publishers can use its CamelCase unit names, such as "
